{"content": "I need to multiply 248\u2089 \u00d7 176\u2089.\n\n**Step 1: Convert to base 10**\n\n248\u2089 = 2\u00d79\u00b2 + 4\u00d79\u00b9 + 8\u00d79\u2070 = 2\u00d781 + 4\u00d79 + 8\u00d71 = 162 + 36 + 8 = 206\u2081\u2080\n\n176\u2089 = 1\u00d79\u00b2 + 7\u00d79\u00b9 + 6\u00d79\u2070 = 1\u00d781 + 7\u00d79 + 6\u00d71 = 81 + 63 + 6 = 150\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Multiply in base 10**\n\n206 \u00d7 150 = 30,900\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Convert result to base 9**\n\n30900 \u00f7 9 = 3433 r 3\n3433 \u00f7 9 = 381 r 4\n381 \u00f7 9 = 42 r 3\n42 \u00f7 9 = 4 r 6\n4 \u00f7 9 = 0 r 4\n\nReading from bottom to top: 46343\u2089\n\n**Step 4: Verification**\n\n46343\u2089 = 4\u00d79\u2074 + 6\u00d79\u00b3 + 3\u00d79\u00b2 + 4\u00d79\u00b9 + 3\u00d79\u2070 = 4\u00d76561 + 6\u00d7729 + 3\u00d781 + 4\u00d79 + 3\u00d71 = 26244 + 4374 + 243 + 36 + 3 = 30900\u2081\u2080 \u2713\n\n46343", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 1150, "completion_tokens": 424}